# ----------------------------------------------------------------
# BREAKDOWN SHORTS ENGINE (alt_inplay_breakdown_v1) — ENABLED
# Backtest BTC+ETH+SOL: trades=192 net=+36.09% PF=1.922 WR=54.7% DD=3.33% neg_months=0
# Backtest 6 coins (breakdown_expansion_v1 best): net=+81.22% PF=2.118 WR=57.4% DD=4.8%
# Decision 2026-03-26: expanded to 6 coins (BTC+ETH+SOL+LINK+ATOM+LTC)
# Monthly: 10/12 green, stronger PF, doubled net PnL vs 3-coin baseline
# ----------------------------------------------------------------
